---
title: Smart Mini Turkey Meatballs and Flatbread Chips with Mint-Cucumber Raita
description: This light plate is loaded with summery flavours  like mint and cucumber. Indian spices punctuate  adorable mini meatballs, while the raita is equally lovely paired with meatballs as it is for dipping the flatbread chips!
